Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_dtknqr1

Device IN Token Sequence Learning Queue Read Register 1 (DTKNQR1)

The depth of the IN Token Sequence Learning Queue is specified for Device Mode IN Token Sequence Learning Queue Depth. The queue is 4 bits wide to store the endpoint number. A read from this register returns the first 5 endpoint entries of the IN Token Sequence Learning Queue. When the queue is full, the new token is pushed into the queue and oldest token is discarded.
